OL,3,C'Red tape' review launched for Welsh
OL,4,Cfarmers
OL,6,FA nine-month 'red tape' review has
OL,7,Fbeen launched in a bid to ease
OL,8,F'bureaucratic burden' on family farms.
OL,10,FLlyr Gruffydd, Minister for Rural
OL,11,FResilience and Sustainability
OL,12,Fannounced the initiative at the Royal
OL,13,FWelsh Grassland event in front of
OL,14,Ffarmers, locals, and business owners.
OL,16,FHe proposes the review will assess
OL,17,Fwhat requirements are necessary for a
OL,18,Ffarming business to survive.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
