OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781387266
OL,3,C'Red tape' review launched for Welsh
OL,4,Cfarmers
OL,6,FWhen asked if this Government will be
OL,7,Fabout reviews and no action, Llyr
OL,8,FGruffydd said: "No, but you have to
OL,9,Fknow what action needs to be taken and
OL,10,Fthat action needs to be grounded in
OL,11,Ffact and it needs to be respectful and
OL,12,Fresponsive to what people are telling
OL,13,Fyou is needed".
OL,15,FHe added: "I am taking an objective
OL,16,Fview here, I am bringing the expert
OL,17,Fin."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
