OL,3,C'Red tape' review launched for Welsh
OL,4,Cfarmers
OL,6,FIndependently chairing the review will
OL,7,Fbe former NFU Cymru President and
OL,8,Ffarmer, John Davies. The farmer based
OL,9,Fin Brecon said: "I know first-hand the
OL,10,Fpressures farmers face in dealing with
OL,11,Fregulation, inspection and
OL,12,Fadministration.
OL,14,F'I am really passionate about the
OL,15,Fenvironment, what I hate is regulation
OL,16,Fgetting in the way."
OL,26,@qD@QOU
