OL,3,C'Red tape' review launched for Welsh
OL,4,Cfarmers
OL,6,FNFU Cymru are welcoming the review and
OL,7,Fappointment of John Davies and believe
OL,8,Fhe has the ability to pursue the role
OL,9,Feffectively. The current NFU Cymru
OL,10,FPresident, Abi Reader said: "John is a
OL,11,Fhugely well-respected figure within
OL,12,Fthe Welsh agricultural industry,
OL,13,Fpossesses an excellent understanding
OL,14,Fof the regulatory landscape and has
OL,15,Fthe knowledge and passion to take this
OL,16,Fimportant area of work forward".
OL,26,@rD@]OUxD@_O]
