OL,3,C'Red tape' review launched for Welsh
OL,4,Cfarmers
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservative's are in
OL,7,Fsupport of the review but also raise
OL,8,Fconcerns. Andrew RT Davies, Shadow
OL,9,FMinister for Farming and Environment,
OL,10,Fsaid: "Any serious effort to cut red
OL,11,Ftape for Welsh farmers is welcome. But
OL,12,Fwe have seen this before.
OL,26,@rD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
