PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1781387266
OL,3,C'Red tape' review launched for Welsh
OL,4,Cfarmers
OL,6,F"New governments often launch these
OL,7,Fkinds of reviews, only to reach the
OL,8,Fend of their term having created a
OL,9,Fwhole load of new red tape that
OL,10,Fstrangles the industry. If this review
OL,11,Fis going to be effective, it needs to
OL,12,Fhappen quickly. Waiting nine months
OL,13,Ffor the review team to present its
OL,14,Freport is painfully slow".
OL,26,@vD@YO]
